Title: Series: Cabinet Poullain
Series: Collection de cent-vingt estampes gravées d'après les tableaux & dessins qui composoient le Cabinet de M. Poullain
Description: Plate 45: Rest on the flight into Egypt, after Solimena: landscape with the Virgin and Child sitting on the left, two angels nearby; on the right, St Joseph tending the bull. c.1781 Etching and engraving
Producer name: Print made by: Robert de Launay
Curator's comments: From 'Cabinet Poullain' (see 1853,1008.355), a set published in 1781.
